text: Movie 43 is an American comedy movie in which Emma Stone, Halle Berry, Hugh Jackman, Uma Thurman, Elizabeth Banks, Chris Pratt, Naomi Watts, Seth MacFarlane, Josh Duhamel, Anna Faris, Greg Kinnear, Dennis Quaid, Kate Winslet, Gerard Butler, Richard Gere, Johnny Knoxville, Justin Long, and many other actors star. Its release date was January 25, 2013, On February 10, 2017, it aired on Teletoon's nighttime programming block, Teletoon at Night, and is rated 18A for sex, romance, nudity, swearing, violence, & sexual content. ==References== Category:2013 comedy movies Category:2010s black comedy movies Category:2010s sex comedy movies Category:American black comedy movies Category:American sex comedy movies Category:English-language movies Category:American independent movies
